  help: Unbounded stack recursion via deeply nested messages

CVE-2024-7254-CLASS

  × Field Tree.Legacy uses deprecated TYPE_GROUP. Known CVE surface (CVE-2024-7254 class). Replace with nested message.
   ╭─[tree.proto:4:5]
 3 │     Tree left = 1;
 4 │     group Legacy = 2;
   ·     ────────┬────────
   ·             ╰── here
 5 │ }
   ╰────
  help: Unbounded recursion via deeply nested TYPE_GROUP (fixed in 3.25.5, 4.27.5, 4.28.2)
